            <summary>How do I build my first investment portfolio?</summary>
            <p>Start by defining your financial goals and risk tolerance, then choose a diversified mix of assets that align with them.</p>
        </details>

        <details>
            <summary>Why is diversification important in a portfolio?</summary>
            <p>Diversification spreads risk across different asset classes, reducing the impact of any single poor-performing investment.</p>
        </details>

